Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.plus.disk

Class HddCloudletSchedulerTimeShared

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletScheduler
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.plus.disk.HddCloudletSchedulerTimeShared
public class HddCloudletSchedulerTimeShared extends CloudletScheduler
HddCloudletSchedulerTimeShared implements a policy of scheduling performed by a virtual machine. Unlike other cloudlet schedulers, this one takes into account the I/O operations required by the cloudlet.

Unlike other CloudletSchedulers this class keeps a reference to the VM, whose cloudlets are scheduled. Thus one needs to set the vm before using an instance of this scheduler.
Adapted from code of:
  • Rodrigo N. Calheiros
  • Anton Beloglazov
